<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:29:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于特朗普关税担忧，亚洲股市走弱；日元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-27/</link><description>亚洲股市周三走高，因投资者担心即将上任的美国总统唐纳德·特朗普可能会针对哪些国家征收关税，一天前他承诺对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收新关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:19:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国可能因总统太平洋访问而在台湾附近举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-could-launch-military-drills-near-taiwan-over-presidents-pacific-visit-2024-11-27/</link><description>根据台湾和地区安全官员的评估，中国可能会在未来几天在台湾附近发动军事演习，以总统赖清德即将前往太平洋和计划过境美国为借口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-could-launch-military-drills-near-taiwan-over-presidents-pacific-visit-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾富士康表示，全球制造足迹使其免受特朗普关税的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwans-foxconn-says-global-manufacturing-footprint-shield-it-trumps-tariffs-2024-11-27/</link><description>台湾富士康周三表示，预计美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普征收新关税对公司的影响将小于其竞争对手，理由是其全球制造业足迹。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:17:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwans-foxconn-says-global-manufacturing-footprint-shield-it-trumps-tariffs-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>英国《金融时报》报道中国国防部长因腐败接受调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-defence-minister-placed-under-investigation-corruption-ft-reports-2024-11-27/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周三报道，中国国防部长董军已接受调查，这是一项范围广泛的反腐败调查的一部分，该调查已经扰乱了中国人民解放军高层。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 02:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-defence-minister-placed-under-investigation-corruption-ft-reports-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体驳回特朗普的关税誓言，重点关注芬太尼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-state-media-dismiss-trumps-tariff-vow-focus-fentanyl-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国官方媒体对美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周二晚间在社论中承诺对中国商品加征关税的言论不屑一顾，指责这位前总统将中国未能解决芬太尼危机的责任归咎于中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 01:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-state-media-dismiss-trumps-tariff-vow-focus-fentanyl-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国恒大投资者强烈抗议，敦促采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/careful-protest-china-evergrandes-investors-press-action-2024-11-27/</link><description>数百名因中国恒大倒闭而损失积蓄的中国投资者本月发起了一场协调一致的运动，向当局施压，要求提供这家倒闭房地产开发商的最新情况。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 01:26:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/careful-protest-china-evergrandes-investors-press-action-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普提议的关税可能如何影响大宗商品和能源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/how-trumps-proposed-tariffs-might-affect-commodities-energy-2024-11-27/</link><description>当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周一承诺对美国三大贸易伙伴——加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收关税。拟议的关税将影响广泛的行业，包括石油、天然气、农业和制造业，有可能改变长期建立的贸易模式和供应链。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 01:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/how-trumps-proposed-tariffs-might-affect-commodities-energy-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：特朗普关税承诺扰乱货币</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-pix-graphic-2024-11-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 21:49:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-pix-graphic-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>出于安全考虑，中国警告新西兰不要加入 AUKUS - 报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-nz-against-joining-aukus-amid-security-concerns-report-2024-11-26/</link><description>中国驻新西兰大使王小龙表示，如果新西兰加入安全组织AUKUS，将“不可避免地”对该国与中国的关系产生负面影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 20:45:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-warns-nz-against-joining-aukus-amid-security-concerns-report-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，特朗普计划根据新关税计划不豁免石油进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/trump-would-impose-25-tariffs-oil-mexico-canada-under-trade-plan-sources-say-2024-11-26/</link><description>消息人士周二告诉路透社，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普并不打算免除对加拿大和墨西哥的原油征收 25% 的进口关税，因为石油行业警告称，该政策可能会损害消费者、工业和国家安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 18:35:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/trump-would-impose-25-tariffs-oil-mexico-canada-under-trade-plan-sources-say-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普获胜后，随着关税的临近，企业加强了货币对冲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/companies-bolster-currency-hedges-after-trump-win-tariffs-loom-2024-11-26/</link><description>跨国公司正在加强外汇对冲策略，以保护其海外收入免受唐纳德·特朗普第二任总统可能带来的更大货币波动的影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 17:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/companies-bolster-currency-hedges-after-trump-win-tariffs-loom-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易伙伴表示，特朗普关税将损害所有相关方</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-trade-partners-warn-trump-tariffs-would-harm-all-involved-2024-11-26/</link><description>墨西哥、加拿大和中国的官员以及主要行业团体警告称，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对商品征收高额关税将损害所有相关国家的经济，导致通胀飙升并损害就业市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 16:57:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-trade-partners-warn-trump-tariffs-would-harm-all-involved-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>分析师和商界领袖对特朗普的北美关税威胁做出反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/analysts-react-trumps-threat-north-american-tariffs-2024-11-26/</link><description>周二，金融分析师和商界领袖对美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁要在 1 月份连任时对主要贸易伙伴墨西哥和加拿大征收 25% 的关税做出反应，此举可能引发贸易战。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 16:25:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/analysts-react-trumps-threat-north-american-tariffs-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>员工称轩尼诗暂停在中国装瓶干邑白兰地的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hennessy-suspends-plan-bottle-cognac-china-say-staff-2024-11-26/</link><description>周二，听取管理层通报的员工表示，法国干邑制造商轩尼诗已暂停在中国装瓶白兰地的计划，以避免进口关税，此前数百名工人上周举行罢工抗议此举。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 14:59:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hennessy-suspends-plan-bottle-cognac-china-say-staff-2024-11-26/</guid></item><item><title>瑞典敦促中国船只返回进行海底电缆调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/sweden-asks-chinese-ship-yi-peng-3-move-swedish-waters-pm-says-2024-11-26/</link><description>瑞典总理乌尔夫·克里斯特森周二表示，瑞典要求一艘中国船只返回瑞典水域，以帮助调查波罗的海最近发生的海底光缆泄露事件，但强调他并没有提出任何指控。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 07:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/sweden-asks-chinese-ship-yi-peng-3-move-swedish-waters-pm-says-2024-11-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>